    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone needing a functional daily driver. Mechanically, the car is sound with a steady engine and a transmission that shifts reliably, though it may not feel as crisp as a newer model. You can expect some cosmetic wear, including minor scratches on the exterior and some fading in the interior upholstery. It has been maintained regularly, but it does show its age and mileage through these visible imperfections. This is a solid, honest car that will get you where you need to go without any major immediate concerns.",
      "price": 21500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
